1st Jail break map release. Tried to keep it simple, fun and nicely textured.
Please let me know if the map has texture problems. As I used a lot of custom made textures so I was forced to use " Map Analyst "


Otherwise Enjoy.

NOTE - If you can not enter the VIP suite. It is because of a filter I have placed on the map. To Try and keep the room VIP. However if this has not worked. Which by knowing my n00b skills as a mapper it hasn't. Then BONUS FOR YOU GUYS. You can has VIP's st00f.
